features: Package content: you will receive 2 pieces of pet bow ties and 5 pieces of necktie collars, 7 pieces in total, sufficient quantity to dress your dog and cat and can meet your replacement needs; They are in different pattern, including solid color, stripe pattern and star pattern

Creative shooting props: these pet bow tie collars can add gentle and elegant touch to your pet and well coordinate with different clothing and accessories; With the help of them, your pet will surely receive tons of compliments from your friends and guest and they can serve as great photo props to let you take impressive photo of your dogs

Polyester material: these adjustable pet neck ties are made of quality material and polyester material, friendly to your pet skin and will not strangle the neck, which can offer them a comfortable wearing experience

Wide application: these puppy grooming ties are delicate and eye-catching accessories for daily wear, photo-taking, parties, weddings, holidays and parties, making your pet stand out among another pet; They are nice option for gift to your friends who raise cat and dog, fit for Chihuahua, Pomeranian, Small Poodle, Yorkshire, Short hair, Persian, Puppet, etc.
